{"tid":2458084,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"淺談香港各大牌子啤酒","createTime":"2021-03-23T07:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T22:12:47.000Z","uid":49163,"like":6,"dislike":137,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"c877fe8cfbf8b3415a6b8e32b85774233e93bef4","tid":2458084,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:11:49.000Z","msg":"青島：苦溼得黎又一大浸廢老味 廢老先飲<br />\n藍冰：得個苦主 同飲24味無分別<br />\n獅威：攻鼻得黎又難飲  廢中廢老先飲<br />\n藍妹：好少少但都係有浸酸縮味 價錢又貴啲<br />\nAsahi：淡茂茂無酒味 細蚊仔先飲<br />\n香港「友」啤酒：價錢公道 入口順滑 清新的麥芽味把啤酒花的微苦平衡得恰到好處。加入芫荽和陳皮等地道材料，透過濃郁果香突出啤酒花香氣，把香港獨有的中西合璧文化發揮得淋漓盡致。<br />\n喜歡飲香港友睇得出係對生活品味有追求既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a69401b1018d18e9162a1c2f1c22c4d426e482","tid":2458084,"uid":49163,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7VqkFj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7VqkFj.jpg&h=41bccea0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf1114e6f681d581b2b82226c3f54dbb7513ff1d","tid":2458084,"uid":41846,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:12:57.000Z","msg":"真！不過少爺好飲啲"},{"pid":"21696d17735acfd5f13d4f7da61dee2e174b719d","tid":2458084,"uid":32028,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cf1114e6f681d581b2b82226c3f54dbb7513ff1d","tid":2458084,"uid":41846,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:12:57.000Z","msg":"真！不過少爺好飲啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"無錯，友真係麻麻"},{"pid":"53e1f2f1d8d7a07ff33538206fc902308c3f9004","tid":2458084,"uid":144541,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:17:16.000Z","msg":"Asahi都冇酒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你條利"},{"pid":"f752e49ebe45ec754299e19a170002c6f351a458","tid":2458084,"uid":56902,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:17:43.000Z","msg":"手工啤: 少爺啤, 麥子, 香港城釀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2